To create the user pablo as a superuser, and assign a password immediately:

cgtest@debian:/var/www/html$ createuser -P -s -e pablo
Enter password for new role:
Enter it again:
CREATE ROLE pablo PASSWORD 'md5556a81062aba566e94da33de0fdc3b86' SUPERUSER CREATEDB CREATEROLE INHERIT LOGIN;
cgtest@debian:/var/www/html$


